```

## ✅ Checklist

Before deploying to production:

- [ ] Set `NODE_ENV=production`
- [ ] Set valid `DATABASE` URL
- [ ] Set strong `JWT_SECRET` (min 32 characters)
- [ ] Set `RESEND_API` with valid key
- [ ] Set `BILLSTACK_APP_EMAIL` with verified domain
- [ ] Test email sending
- [ ] Verify `.env` is in `.gitignore`
- [ ] Never commit `.env` to git
- [ ] Use secrets management (if hosting platform supports it)

## 🚀 Quick Start

1. **Copy this template to `.env`**
2. **Get Resend API key** (5 minutes at https://resend.com)
3. **Fill in your values:**
   ```env
   RESEND_API=re_your_key_here
   BILLSTACK_APP_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
   ```
4. **Restart server:**
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```
5. **Test email sending** (see EMAIL_QUICK_START.md)

